Finance minister says hedges cost
$450m at event in Mexico City.
* Videgaray says reviewing whether to modify hedges for new
$85/bbl oil price
* Oil exports ‘completely’ covered at $81/bbl
* Videgaray says decision to hedge through $85/bbl to depend on
hedge prices and oil and future prices.
* NOTE: Congress changed oil price hedge from $81 to $85 in 2014
budget plan
* NOTE: Govt buys oil hedges to protect budget versus short-term
